4.00	Dead_End_(Angel_episode)	Dead End (Angel)	"Dead End" is episode 18 of season 2 in the television show Angel. Written by David Greenwalt and directed by James A. Contner, it was originally broadcast on April 24, 2001 on the WB television network. In "Dead End", Lindsey receives a new hand from Wolfram &amp; Hart, which appears to have an evil agenda of its own. Angel and Lindsey independently discover that Wolfram &amp; Hart forcefully removes limbs from people to obtain transplants, and work together to destroy the clinic responsible. Disillusioned, Lindsey leaves Los Angeles.	
